        "description": "**This is an Early Access version for Quest**\nWe are grateful for all your enthusiasm and tremendous support! Your support isn't just a purchase; it's a key to unlocking the future of the Grimlord universe. We are working tirelessly to push the project to the full release in 2024!\n{1470623396971318}\nABOUT\nStarting from the most basic beginnings, strive to rise above your circumstances. You have complete freedom in how you fight, endless possibilities for crafting, and you'll face a variety of challenging foes. Your destiny and the fate of this land depend on your actions.\nThis is a narrative-focused action RPG designed specifically for virtual reality. This experience has been long awaited. \nThis is Grimlord.\n{339542969245098}\nKEY FEATURES\n* Creative Combat Styles - Hold your weapon wherever you want. However, you want, and use real-life fighting styles to defeat your foe.\n* Weaponry Customization - Dozens of weapon parts to unlock and hundreds of combinations\n{855445876653632}\n* Variety of Enemies & Epic Boss Fight \n* Immerse into a good-ole Souls-style map loop.\n{1267353814262955}\n\n\n{489162720621683}\n",
